  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the urinary excretion and renal metabolism of
      vitamins, in particular vitamin B12 and folate, in relation to various renal conditions
      involving loss of renal function and/or proteinuria.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
